    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> favors nov<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> 22<hi rend="superscript">d.</hi> 28<hi rend="superscript">th.</hi> 29<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> came safe. all acceptable. There is an excellent
                        <rs type="art" ref="ar0128">head of Beaton</rs> in the <placeName ref="pl0724">Hamilton Lodgings Holyrood house</placeName>. I saw it with
                    these very eyes.</p>
                <p><persName ref="pe0203">Mr Mackenzies</persName> kind Letter is here
                        answered.<note type="editorial">See Pennant's letter to John Mackenzie on <ref target="0404.xml">7 December 1774</ref>.</note></p>
                <p>Why will <persName ref="pe0076">doctor Blinshall</persName> retard matters. but
                    no more of that.</p>
                <p><persName ref="pe0233">My relation</persName> is better I set off for <placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName> on Saturday. Write to me <placeName ref="pl1647">N<hi rend="superscript">o</hi> 11 Vere Street Oxford
                        chapel</placeName> &amp; never mind franks.</p>
                <p><persName ref="pe0157">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Macgovan</persName> is like
                    many of y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> countrymen most hospitable &amp; good to
                    friends in sight. <persName ref="pe0022">Doctor Ramsay</persName> d<hi rend="superscript">o.</hi> He did promise a sketch of the Danish monum<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> in <placeName ref="pl0367">Inch colme</placeName>
                    but alas Love absorbs everything.</p>
                <closer><salute>I am Dear Sir <lb/>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> very sincere
                        <lb/>humble Serv<hi rend="superscript">t.</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant.</persName></signed>

                <dateline>Downing Dec<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> 7<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>
                    1774.</dateline></closer>
            </div>
        </body>
